hands_on_practices.solution:
我们在 $r_b$ 处应用史瓦西判据：
$$\nabla_{\rm rad}\;\equiv\;\frac{d\ln T}{d\ln P}
=\frac{3\,\kappa\,P\,L}{16\pi a c G M_r T^4}
\;\stackrel{!}{=}\;\nabla_{\rm ad}
=\frac{\gamma-1}{\gamma}
=\frac{2}{5}\,.$$
在边界处，$M_r=M_b$，$P=P_b$，$T=T_b$，且 $\kappa=\kappa_0\rho_bT_b^{-\alpha}$。  
使用对流绝热关系 $P_b=K\,T_b^{5/2}$ 和理想气体定律
$$P_b=\frac{\rho_b k_B T_b}{\mu m_H}
\quad\Longrightarrow\quad
\rho_b=\frac{\mu m_H\,P_b}{k_B T_b}
=\frac{\mu m_H\,K\,T_b^{5/2}}{k_B T_b}
=\frac{\mu m_H\,K}{k_B}\,T_b^{3/2}\,,$$
我们发现
$$\kappa_b=\kappa_0\,\rho_b\,T_b^{-\alpha}
=\kappa_0\frac{\mu m_H\,K}{k_B}T_b^{3/2-\alpha}\,.$$
代入 $\nabla_{\rm rad}=2/5$：

$$
\frac{3\,L}{16\pi a c G M_b}\,\kappa_b\,P_b\,T_b^{-4}
=\frac{2}{5}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
\frac{3L}{16\pi a c G M_b}
\Bigl[\kappa_0\frac{\mu m_H K}{k_B}T_b^{3/2-\alpha}\Bigr]
\bigl[K\,T_b^{5/2}\bigr]T_b^{-4}
=\frac{2}{5}\,.
$$

合并 $T_b$ 的幂次：
$$T_b^{3/2-\alpha+5/2-4}=T_b^{(3/2+5/2)-4-\alpha}=T_b^{-\alpha}\,.$$
因此
$$\frac{3L\,\kappa_0\,\mu m_H\,K^2}{16\pi a c G M_b\,k_B}\,T_b^{-\alpha}
=\frac{2}{5}
\quad\Longrightarrow\quad
T_b^{-\alpha}
=\frac{2}{5}\frac{16\pi a c G M_b\,k_B}{3L\,\kappa_0\,\mu m_H\,K^2}
=\frac{32\pi a c G M_b\,k_B}{15L\,\kappa_0\,\mu m_H\,K^2}\,.
$$
反转并取 $1/\alpha$ 次幂，得到结果：
$$
T_b
=\left(\frac{15\,L\,\kappa_0\,\mu m_H\,K^2}{32\pi a c G M_b\,k_B}\right)^{1/\alpha}\,. 
$$
